data.description: Beautiful, 3 bed 2 bath plus office/den or bonus room 2 car garage, nestled on just over an acre in a country setting with lots of room on all 4 sides of home and fenced back yard with Back covered screened porch. Some updates to mention New vinyl Plank floors with baseboards in majority of home, freshly painted interior, Roof and Exterior Paint  2021, Well filtration system 2023, This community is conveniently located in East Orlando, only a 25 minute drive to MCO Airport. 35 minute drive to the actual beach at Cocoa Beach. 30 minute drive to the heart of downtown Orlando. This community features: A newly built K-8 Wedgefield School, Club House and restaurant, picnic pavilion, tot lot, skate park, sports court.  Don't miss out on this opportunity!! Call for your private showing today!!
